{{> header}}
<h1>Your role in {{orgName}} has changed</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}}, your role in <strong>{{orgName}}</strong> has been updated.</p>
<div class="card">
  <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{orgName}}</p>
  <p><strong>Previous role:</strong> <span class="tag">{{oldRole}}</span></p>
  <p><strong>New role:</strong> &nbsp;<span class="badge {{#if (eq newRole "admin")}}badge-admin{{else if (eq newRole "owner")}}badge-owner{{else}}badge-member{{/if}}">{{newRole}}</span></p>
</div>
{{#if (eq newRole "admin")}}
<p>As an <strong>Admin</strong> you can now create and delete boards, invite members, and manage roles within the organization.</p>
{{else if (eq newRole "owner")}}
<p>As the <strong>Owner</strong> you have full control over the organization, including settings and deletion.</p>
{{else}}
<p>As a <strong>Member</strong> you can view boards, create tasks, and collaborate with your team.</p>
{{/if}}
<p style="text-align:center;margin:28px 0;">
  <a href="{{orgUrl}}" class="btn">Go to {{orgName}}</a>
</p>
{{> footer}}
